=Description=

"The Open Source Beehives project is a collaborative response to the threat faced by bee populations in industrialised nations around the world. We design hives that can support bee colonies in a sustainable way, to monitor and track the health and behaviour of a colony as it develops. Each hive contains an open source sensory kit, The Smart Citizen Kit, which can transmit to an open data platform: smartcitizen.me The OSBH project is a collaboration between Open Tech Forever and Fab Lab Barcelona."
(http://blog.liv.io/575/opensourcebeehives/)


